In this code, you need to create a custom arrow image file with the desired appearance and save it in the "MQL4\Images" directory. Then, set the "ArrowName" property to the filename (without the file extension) of the custom image you created.

Note: The custom arrow image file should be a PNG image with transparency enabled and should have dimensions of 64x64 pixels.

